pictures to prove it.

00:50:40.300 --> 00:50:43.990
And I feel like that's
part of the message that

00:50:43.990 --> 00:50:46.540
resonates with people
is, oh, wait, really?

00:50:46.540 --> 00:50:48.280
Those people aren't
living the life

00:50:48.280 --> 00:50:49.780
that they say they're
living either?

